cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques for photo-sketch generation. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach for end-to-end learning using a fully convolutional network, which falls under the category of deep learning and neural networks. This suggests that the paper could also be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia (MM) data, specifically face photos and sketches, which could classify it under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper also discusses face sketch verification, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another possible sub-category.
